        <div class="author-avatar">R</div>
        <p><strong>A note from Robert:</strong> I'm 64. I've had conversations with hundreds of men in their 50s and 60s who are frustrated — they're showing up, they're trying, and they're not moving. Almost every time, the conversation comes back to the same place. Not effort. Not age. Not even the workout. It's protein. And they had no idea.</p>
